{
  "stem": "1496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So some of the people from Schindler's factory actually were assigned to this kind of work to clean up this camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this was a horrible time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was lucky that we were working in Schindler's factory to disassemble the machinery and put on the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "By the way, I will mention one other thing-- an incident.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What happened while I was there working to disassemble the machines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One day, we-- what happened-- a plane was shot by the Nazis and split in half.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And half of the plane fell into the camp and the other half on the outside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And while we were-- the, the plane fell in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A fire started, and one of the barracks was on fire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Luckily, this one was the barrack where the people already left to go to Krakau-Plaszow was empty.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Otherwise, the few people-- probably some people would be killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were-- we started to put out the fire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And after we put out the fire, I noticed there was still a pilot sitting in a little chair.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And his head was burned off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "His arms were burned off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "However, on the arm, I noticed an insignia, which was written Australia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so we figured out that this must be one of the English planes which was shot down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "After a while, the Nazis came in, they chased us away, and they start investigating.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Four years ago, when I was in Poland with my wife and my son, we went to Schindler's factory, and I tried to get in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They wouldn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the guard at the gate was talking to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told him about this incident.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, by the way, you know what?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now I believe you that you were here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because-- come over with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
